,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"767b329df62b42d69633c1a6f1d84388b74029b4","tid":2296621,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bbb7356ee1148b26051a37e910fbc839ca5f6c8","tid":2296621,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T23:29:59.000Z","msg":"刀叉擺碟唔一定係食完喎<br />\n要睇擺法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T23:39:27.000Z","msg":"應該左搭右定右搭左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T23:47:10.000Z","msg":"用餐中，有事而離席時，必須把刀叉擺成八字型放在餐盤上。<br />\n用餐結束後，則是平行的斜放在五點鐘位。"},{"pid":"04e21e945afef0e5c3ab879d5af6fa7245a821ee","tid":2296621,"uid":274732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T23:57:35.000Z","msg":"我都試過<br />\n係澳門唔知邊間新酒店<br />\n食到一半返番枱坐滿左4個大陸人<br />\n又收左我套刀叉<br />\n即刻屌個經理開番張新枱比我"},{"pid":"b8cc243c4d8429917186c63a47ce5fa2e45b1fcf","tid":2296621,"uid":155874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bb9bcd5315585b1ab5f36da3561c2016d87362d","tid":2296621,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"767b329df62b42d69633c1a6f1d84388b74029b4","tid":2296621,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bbb7356ee1148b26051a37e910fbc839ca5f6c8","tid":2296621,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T23:29:59.000Z","msg":"刀叉擺碟唔一定係食完喎<br />\n要睇擺法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T23:39:27.000Z","msg":"應該左搭右定右搭左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T23:47:10.000Z","msg":"用餐中，有事而離席時，必須把刀叉擺成八字型放在餐盤上。<br />\n用餐結束後，則是平行的斜放在五點鐘位。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:00:35.000Z","msg":"普通西餐ok<br />\n自助餐出得去拎嘢, 通常都係食晒先出去拎<br />\n擺八字正常代表仲食緊唔可以收碟<br />\n返到位d 人見到隻碟冇比人收到又投訴㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n或者可以考慮將餐巾放係坐位上面"},{"pid":"bb65377eaaa7bcdae111ad7ef1d90bddda6592a4","tid":2296621,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8cc243c4d8429917186c63a47ce5fa2e45b1fcf","tid":2296621,"uid":155874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bb9bcd5315585b1ab5f36da3561c2016d87362d","tid":2296621,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot